Michelada-recipe
shake tajin onto a plate
use a lemon wedge to put lemon juice around rim of a cup
put cup upside down into plate with tajin to get tajin on rim
shake tajin into cup
pour 1/2 cup of lemon juice into cup
pour 1/2 cup of lime juice into cup
a splash of worcestshire sauce
a couple of splashes of tapatio
pour chamoy along inside of cup
3 cups of clamato
12 oz of mexican beer (modelo prefered)